author: Gabby Orr
title: ‘We don’t want to be tone-deaf’: Trump allies test coronavirus messaging
description: A push by the president to unleash the economy is creating nightmares among some close supporters.
content:
America First, the primary super PAC dedicated to Trumps reelection, began asking respondents in a series of polls this week if they fear catching the virus more than losing their jobs, according to a person familiar with the effort.
